== Town Twinning ==
Reykjav<U+00ED>k is twinned with the following:
* [[Image:Flag of the United Kingdom.svg|25px]] [[Kingston upon Hull]], [[United Kingdom]]
* [[Image:Flag of the United States.svg|25px]] [[Seattle, Washington]], [[United States]]
* [[Image:Flag of Canada.svg|25px]] [[Winnipeg, Manitoba]], [[Canada]]
* [[Image:Flag of Lithuania.svg|25px]] [[Vilnius]], [[Lithuania]]

